%h2 #{behavior.symbol} (e.g. #{behavior.eg})
=render behavior.example_path
-if @realm || @behavior.is_a?(Phase)
  %p.left
    Compulsive #{behavior.name} (e.g. can’t stop #{behavior.eg.ing}) when you don’t
    =behavior.manic? ? "have enough" : "need the"
    #{behavior.realm.word} #{behavior.noun.word} is
    %b=behavior.severity
    =link_to behavior.episode.wrap, behavior.answer_path
    and makes you #{behavior.imbalance}.
